Package: roboparty-imu
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, roboparty-base (>= 1.0.0)
Description: RoboParty IMU driver
 IMU driver with HIPNUC support (CAN and serial protocols).
 Provides static libraries, headers and Python bindings.
 Installs udev rules for IMU serial devices.
